description: A good night to go out in Prague. And a good test for my new camera. I decided to go to the red-light district in Holesovice. I spent some time there before I saw a quite young guy leaving one of the venues. I asked him if he could recommend a special club. He told me that girls in that club are quite nice and cheap. Nice and cheap? Well, I asked him if he would company me to search for another club. He was ready to party. But he was broke now. A good opportunity for me to offer him fast money. He was worried about my cam. Well, thats not unusual. So I started slow and I offered him 2.000 if he would show me his bare chest here and now. It was a funny night and a Chinese lady interrupted us.
title: Czech Hunter 23
